{{Infobox scientist |name = Ronald Micura |image = |image_size = |caption = Ronald Micura |birth_date = |birth_place = |residence = |nationality = |death_date = |death_place = |field = [[biochemistry]] |work_institution = |alma_mater = [[University of Linz]] |doctoral_advisor = |doctoral_students = |known_for = |prizes = [[Lieben Prize]] |religion = |footnotes = }}''' Ronald Micura''' is an Austrian chemist. He was awarded the [[Lieben Prize]] in 2005.
